dict.string: An excellent one-click EFI configuration tool based on OpenCore
Generic USBX device for USB power properties
Sets plugin-type to 1 on first Processor object
SSDT to disable USB RHUB/HUBN/URTH and rename devices
Defines PNLF device with a _UID of 19 for backlight control - requires PNLF to XNLF rename
_OSI override to return true through Windows 11, version 22H2 - requires _OSI to XOSI rename
Defines an MCHC and BUS0 device for SMBus compatibility
